name: Cyberse Whitehat
desc: If you control 2 or more monsters with the same Type, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand). You can only Special Summon "Cyberse Whitehat" once per turn this way. If this card is sent to the GY as material for a Link Summon: You can make all monsters your opponent controls lose 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.
